---
const title = "Stakater | Red Hat Growth Partner";
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
<title>{title}</title>

<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
:root {
  --primary: #E00000;
  --dark: #0A0F1C;
  --gray: #6B7280;
  --light: #F5F7FA;
  --gradient: linear-gradient(135deg, #E00000 0%, #7A0000 100%);
}

* { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

html, body {
  height: 100%;
  overflow: hidden;
  font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
  background: white;
  color: var(--dark);
}

.slide-container {
  height: 100vh;
  width: 100vw;
  overflow: hidden;
  position: relative;
}

.slides {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  transition: transform 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.77, 0, 0.175, 1);
}

section {
  height: 100vh;
  padding: 100px 60px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  position: relative;
}

.container {
  max-width: 1100px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

h1 { font-size: 60px; font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.1; }
h2 { font-size: 44px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 20px; }
h3 { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; }

p  { font-size: 20px; color: var(--gray); max-width: 900px; }

.highlight { color: var(--primary); font-weight: 700; }

.section-light { background: var(--light); }

.logo {
  position: fixed;
  top: 30px;
  left: 50px;
  font-weight: 800;
  letter-spacing: 3px;
  font-size: 18px;
  z-index: 1000;
}

.nav-dots {
  position: fixed;
  right: 30px;
  top: 50%;
  transform: translateY(-50%);
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 12px;
  z-index: 1000;
  opacity: 0;
  transition: opacity 0.4s ease;
}

.nav-dots.visible { opacity: 1; }

.dot {
  width: 12px;
  height: 12px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: #d1d5db;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.dot.active {
  background: var(--primary);
  transform: scale(1.3);
}

.metric {
  font-size: 70px;
  font-weight: 800;
  background: var(--gradient);
  -webkit-background-clip: text;
  -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
}

.cta {
  background: var(--gradient);
  color: white;
}

.cta p { color: #ffe5e5; }

.subtle-bg {
  position: absolute;
  width: 600px;
  height: 600px;
  background: radial-gradient(circle at center, rgba(224,0,0,0.08), transparent 70%);
  top: -200px;
  right: -200px;
  animation: float 12s ease-in-out infinite;
}

@keyframes float {
  0% { transform: translateY(0px); }
  50% { transform: translateY(40px); }
  100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="logo">STAKATER</div>

<div class="slide-container">
  <div class="slides" id="slides">

    <section>
      <div class="subtle-bg"></div>
      <div class="container">
        <h1>From Subscription Sale<br/>To Platform Standardization<br/>To Portfolio Expansion</h1>
        <br/>
        <p>
        We help Red Hat sales teams protect ARR, increase node consumption,
        and turn installed OpenShift clusters into strategic, expanding platforms.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-light">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Most OpenShift Accounts Don’t Fail.</h2>
        <h2 class="highlight">They Just Stop Growing.</h2>
        <br/>
        <p>
        Subscription sold. Cluster installed. Engagement ends.
        Adoption slows. Expansion stalls.
        </p>
        <br/>
        <p class="highlight">Installed ≠ Standardized ≠ Strategic</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <div class="container">
        <h2>The Structural Gap</h2>
        <br/>
        <p>
        Customers need continuous operational coaching,
        governance models, internal enablement,
        and workload acceleration.
        </p>
        <br/>
        <p>
        Without this, OpenShift remains tactical — not the enterprise platform it was meant to become.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-light">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>How We Drive Footprint Growth</h2>
        <br/>
        <div class="metric">4</div>
        <p>Expansion vectors per strategic account</p>
        <br/>
        <p>
        Increase workload density → More nodes<br/>
