        Standardize platform → Additional clusters
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Proven Expansion Stories</h2>
        <br/>
        <p><span class="highlight">ATG</span> – 7-year sustained OpenShift growth journey</p>
        <p><span class="highlight">CSN</span> – Introduced ODF and expanding into AMQ Streams</p>
        <p><span class="highlight">Windsor Region</span> – 1 → 2 clusters, added ODF and expanded stack</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-light">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>8 Years of Strategic Red Hat Alignment</h2>
        <br/>
        <p>
        Service Provider Program → CCSP → MSA → Specialized Partner
        </p>
        <br/>
        <p class="highlight">
        Our growth aligns directly with Red Hat’s subscription expansion.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Full Lifecycle Capability</h2>
        <br/>
        <p>
        Day 0 – Architecture<br/>
        Day 1 – Implementation<br/>
        Day 2–1000 – Operational maturity & expansion
        </p>
        <br/>
        <p class="highlight">Our differentiator is continuity.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Let’s Close Sale 2, 3, and 4 Together</h2>
        <br/>
